SELECT 
    JEST_OBJNR, 
    CAST(collect_list(all STAT) AS string) AS STAT_LIST, 
    CAST(collect_list(all TXT04) AS string) AS TXT04_LIST  
FROM 
    in0 
GROUP BY JEST_OBJNR
